      "section": "Define the Index for the dateFacet Type",
      "content": "{\n  \"mappings\": {\n    \"dynamic\": true|false,\n    \"fields\": {\n      \"<field-name>\": {\n        \"type\": \"stringFacet\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}",
